{"id":83146,"date":"2021-11-14T12:03:07","date_gmt":"2021-11-14T06:33:07","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/?p=83146"},"modified":"2021-11-25T12:10:35","modified_gmt":"2021-11-25T06:40:35","slug":"rehnuma-bhati","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/rehnuma-bhati\/","title":{"rendered":"Rehnuma Bhati Wiki, Age, Husband, Family, Biography &amp; More"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Rehnuma-Bhati__.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-83418 \" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Rehnuma-Bhati__.jpg\" alt=\"Rehnuma Bhati\" width=\"406\" height=\"757\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Rehnuma-Bhati__.jpg 429w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Rehnuma-Bhati__-161x300.jpg 161w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 406px) 100vw, 406px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Rehnuma Bhati, an Indian homemaker, is the wife of Riyaz Bhati, who is allegedly a gangster and close aide of famous Indian gangster Dawood Ibrahim. In November 2021, Rehnuma made headlines for accusing her husband of coercing her into having sexual relationships with some famous cricketers, sportspersons, and politicians.<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_62 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Contents<\/p>\n<label for=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce1dd19c58\" class=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-label\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\"  id=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce1dd19c58\"  aria-label=\"Toggle\" \/><nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/rehnuma-bhati\/#WikiBiography\" title=\"Wiki\/Biography\">Wiki\/Biography<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/rehnuma-bhati\/#Physical_Appearance\" title=\"Physical Appearance\">Physical Appearance<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/rehnuma-bhati\/#Family\" title=\"Family\">Family<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/rehnuma-bhati\/#Husband_Children\" title=\"Husband &amp; Children\">Husband &amp; Children<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/rehnuma-bhati\/#Sexual_Assault_Scandal\" title=\"Sexual Assault Scandal\">Sexual Assault Scandal<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"WikiBiography\"><\/span>Wiki\/Biography<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Rehnuma Bhati was born on Friday, 22 July 1988 (<strong>age 33 years; as of 2021<\/strong>). Bhati was born and brought up in Mumbai, and her zodiac sign is Cancer.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Physical_Appearance\"><\/span>Physical Appearance<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Height (approx.):<\/strong> 5&#8242; 3&#8243;<\/p>\n<p><strong>Hair Colour: <\/strong>Black<\/p>\n<p><strong>Eye Colour:\u00a0<\/strong>Grey<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Family\"><\/span>Family<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Husband_Children\"><\/span><strong>Husband &amp; Children<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>She is married to Riyaz Bhati, who is a suspected Indian gangster and allegedly a close aide of Dawood Ibrahim.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_83420\" style=\"width: 451px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Rehnuma-Bhatis-husband-Riyaz-Bhati.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-83420\" class=\" wp-image-83420\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Rehnuma-Bhatis-husband-Riyaz-Bhati.jpg\" alt=\"Rehnuma Bhati's husband Riyaz Bhati\" width=\"441\" height=\"261\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Rehnuma-Bhatis-husband-Riyaz-Bhati.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Rehnuma-Bhatis-husband-Riyaz-Bhati-300x177.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Rehnuma-Bhatis-husband-Riyaz-Bhati-768x454.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 441px) 100vw, 441px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-83420\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Rehnuma Bhati&#8217;s husband Riyaz Bhati<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Rehnuma has two sons named Abdullah Bhati and Ibrahim Bhati.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_83421\" style=\"width: 317px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Rehnuma-Bhati-with-her-sons.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-83421\" class=\" wp-image-83421\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Rehnuma-Bhati-with-her-sons.jpg\" alt=\"Rehnuma Bhati with her sons\" width=\"307\" height=\"425\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Rehnuma-Bhati-with-her-sons.jpg 577w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Rehnuma-Bhati-with-her-sons-216x300.jpg 216w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 307px) 100vw, 307px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-83421\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Rehnuma Bhati with her sons<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Sexual_Assault_Scandal\"><\/span>Sexual Assault Scandal<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>In 2016, reportedly, after the couple split and Rehnuma started living separately from her husband, she was allegedly kidnapped and forced into prostitution again in 2019. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_83146_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_83146_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_83146_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_83146_1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_83146_1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.newsbytesapp.com\/news\/india\/wife-of-dawood-s-aide-alleges-rape-by-pandya\/story\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Newsbytes<\/a><\/span><\/span> In 2021, reports emerged stating that Rehnuma filed a complaint at the Santacruz Police Station in Mumbai, and in her application dated 24 September 2021, Bhati accused her husband of forcing her into having sexual relations with a man in 2011-2012. She added in the application that Riyaz coerced her to have sex with several of his business associates and other \u201chigh-profile\u201d people including prominent cricketers like Hardik Pandya and Munaf Patel. She also named Indian National Congress politician Rajeev Shukla, who has also served as the Vice President of the Board of Control for Cricket in India (BCCI). Another name, Prithviraj Kothari, the MD of RSBL, has also been mentioned in the complaint.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_83162\" style=\"width: 381px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Complaint-filed-by-Rehnuma-Bhati.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-83162\" class=\" wp-image-83162\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Complaint-filed-by-Rehnuma-Bhati.jpg\" alt=\"Complaint filed by Rehnuma Bhati\" width=\"371\" height=\"585\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Complaint-filed-by-Rehnuma-Bhati.jpg 507w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Complaint-filed-by-Rehnuma-Bhati-190x300.jpg 190w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 371px) 100vw, 371px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-83162\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Complaint filed by Rehnuma Bhati<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Publications that had access to Rehnuma&#8217;s complaint reported that her application did not contain\u00a0any address or specific date or place\u00a0where the alleged sexual assault happened. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_83146_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_83146_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_83146_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_83146_1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[2]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_83146_1_2\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/theprint.in\/india\/wife-of-dawood-aide-claims-husband-forced-her-into-sex-work-names-hardik-pandya-rajeev-shukla\/764676\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">ThePrint<\/a><\/span><\/span> Talking about her complaint in an interview, Rehnuma said,<\/p>\n<blockquote><p>I was told to give some money, but why should I spread corruption? I am right in my place. They are the ones who are criminals.\u201d<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p>Two months after her complaint at the police station, Rehnuma publicly accused her husband of forcing her into prostitution for over 15 years. Bhati also disclosed that her husband, Riyaz, blackmailed her with her sensitive photos and videos, and threatened to kill her and their two children if she refused to comply with his demands; however, no FIR was registered. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_83146_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_83146_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_83146_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_83146_1_3\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[3]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_83146_1_3\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.shethepeople.tv\/news\/rehnuma-bhati-rape-case-heres-all-you-need-to-know\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">SheThePeople<\/a><\/span><\/span> Rehnuma added in an interview,<\/p>\n<blockquote><p>I have been trying to get police to register an FIR, but they aren\u2019t complying. My application was submitted in September, it is already November now.&#8221;<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<div class=\"489bcfb86580b123547338c91db0eff2\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"float: none; margin:3px 0 3px 0; text-align:center;\">\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\r\n     style=\"display:block\"\r\n     data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\"\r\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6769524711517462\"\r\n     data-ad-slot=\"2473600074\"><\/ins>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 0px; height: 0px; line-height: 0px; margin: 0; padding: 0; clear: both;\"><\/div><div class=\"speaker-mute footnot